{"tid":1598564,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［正字特警］DNLM v. DLLM","createTime":"2019-09-27T14:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T15:02:18.000Z","uid":45906,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1c5ddd15b4c94dbf42bf8e72d53a7513bdeee471","tid":1598564,"uid":45906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:01:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xh3txeu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXh3txeu.png&h=52173ba8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n醬油：中大粵語審音配詞字庫<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解每次見到DLLM都會有啲嗱住嗱住，<br />\n啱啱見到有隧道有人大大隻字噴咗DLLM，我就同大家討論吓：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：一直用咗咁耐，DLLM就DLLM啦。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：正字就係正字，一定要改返DNLM。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n十月一見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"5c70d152befbe9fed66d27cff796b7920db9bd09","tid":1598564,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:11:00.000Z","msg":"懶音<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b4baf4cd8a0a5713b643585d5b104b9ef4aebab","tid":1598564,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:12:31.000Z","msg":"DKLM實冇錯"},{"pid":"e5e919ead50ccabe95473a6145e9fdb6904615e4","tid":1598564,"uid":201649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:13:21.000Z","msg":"一直都係用DNLM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90bb22954c35239447751c896486d704d80c9bf0","tid":1598564,"uid":284304,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:13:31.000Z","msg":"DNLM會變大陸拼音 政治不正確"},{"pid":"a810dbfc545c197e50bbee3f271f786a4a274f8c","tid":1598564,"uid":244649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:43:30.000Z","msg":"「DLLM」，粵語粗口「屌你老母」的不正統縮寫，漢語為「肏你媽的」。「DLLM」取自「屌你老母」羅馬拼音的聲母Diu Lei Lo Mo。其中「你」字應發鼻音，即「Nei」。故正寫應為「DNLM」。"},{"pid":"aa41d993a7b50df1907217edb5769076653b280a","tid":1598564,"uid":45906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90bb22954c35239447751c896486d704d80c9bf0","tid":1598564,"uid":284304,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:13:31.000Z","msg":"DNLM會變大陸拼音 政治不正確"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T15:02:18.000Z","msg":"大咩陸拼音<br />\nNei明明係粵拼<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}